{
  "stem": "6777.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At that time-- So the bandits-- sorry-- were Poles, were they?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, it was very common in Warsaw, the robberies, like-- like it is here today, or even more.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My friends from the resistance, which have been still friends from Kalisz, from the time when we lived in Kalisz.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Another queer coincidence-- as I told you before, my uncle was a president of the town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And has provided jobs for the caretaker's children in-- one was a message boy, and the other one was something else in the magistrate, as it was called, town hall.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we became real friends with his kids.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And during the war, they came to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then there was another little-- another girl, who was a year behind me at school and whom I have been helping with her school work.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we also became friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they came to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they joined the Polish resistance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they have been my friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These people have taken care of all sort of things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a coincidence-- this family, some of them have been left in Kalisz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But some, the older one, came into Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one girl got taken by force to a-- a work camp in Germany to workers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a camp to which Roman came to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she recognized him, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she said to me much later, after the war, I have seen correspondence coming to him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Roman was his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Eva was on the envelope, who has been writing it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, I had no more doubts it's the same Roman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she helped him all through the time when they've been in the same workers' camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
